reports.description: Dynamic analysis on Microsoft Windows XP

malicious_activity: Autostart: Registering for autostart during Windows boot
Evasion: Possibly stalling against analysis environment (sleep)
Evasion: Trying to detect analysis virtual environment (guest modules detection)
Evasion: Trying to enumerate security products installed on the system from WMI
File: Modifying executable in suspicious location of application data directory
Memory: Replacing the image of a process with the same original executable (potential unpacking)
Network: Connecting to server using hard-coded IP address
